Soon, PuppyRoni will establish partnerships with local pizzerias, hosting PuppyRoni Nights. Holders of $RONI tokens can participate in these nights and enjoy discounts on their favourite pizzas as long as they are members of The Pack. These benefits will only grow as we secure more partnerships and unveil even larger deals.
